*Išao* je kući preko parka. (He went home through the park.)

Kiša je počela da pada dok je on *išao*. (It started raining while he was going.)

On je *išao* u školu svaki dan. (He went to school every day.)

Njegova majka ga je *išla* ispratiti. (His mother went to see him off.)

On je *išao* u prodavnicu po hranu. (He went to the store for food.)

*Išli* su u kino tog popodneva. (They went to the movies that afternoon.)

Njegovi prijatelji su *išli* da ga pozdrave. (His friends went to say goodbye to him.)

*Išla* je u grad da kupi nešto. (She went to town to buy something.)

Oni su *išli* u planinu da se prošetaju. (They went to the mountains for a walk.)